Test Steps

Login as Contractor and navigate to the Decisions page.

Verify only Approved decisions are visible.

Login as FTE and navigate to the Decisions page.

Verify all accessible decisions are visible.

Perform sorting, filtering, and search on the datatable.

Check lazy loading by scrolling down.

Attempt an action without permission or invalid status.

Expected Result

Contractors see only Approved decisions.

FTEs see all accessible decisions.

Datatable shows columns: Name, Status, Decision Reason, Stage, Estimated Decision Date.

Sorting, filtering, search, and lazy load work correctly.

Unauthorized actions are disabled.

Retry banner appears when errors occur.
